</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Device_Event</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>indicates it&apos;s a device event. Should read as 0x00 </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
<parametername>:</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>indicates the type of device event. 0 - DisconnEvt 1 - USBRst 2 - ConnectDone 3 - ULStChng 4 - WkUpEvt 5 - Reserved 6 - EOPF 7 - SOF 8 - Reserved 9 - ErrticErr 10 - CmdCmplt 11 - EvntOverflow 12 - VndrDevTstRcved </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
